wmsLayer.title: GA0334 S 2m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of the southern survey area from marine survey GA0334, collected in the Vlaming Sub-basin, Western Australia. A total of two areas were surveyed to a two metre resolution. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 35-120 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/78540.
